Subscribe to Multiple Shared Collections

To subscribe, click the collection on the CRM Analytics home page, select Subscribe in the menu, and set the schedule. Subscription emails include a link to the collection and direct links to each lens.

Required Editions and User Permissions:
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

User Permissions Needed:
To set subscriptions on CRM Analytics lenses and dashboard widgets: Subscribe to CRM Analytics Assets
To subscribe to tables and receive email with table data in attached .csv files: Download CRM Analytics Data

Subscription Considerations:
You can subscribe to as many as 4 collections, each with its own schedule. Each subscription email can include up to 20 lenses. Dashboards within a collection don’t appear in the subscription email.
A collection subscription is dynamic, which means that adding, reordering, or deleting lenses in the collection is automatically reflected in the subscription email and preview.
Unlike Widget Subscriptions, individual lenses in a collection can’t be deleted in the Subscription Preview. To remove a lens from the subscription, delete it from the collection.
